quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,43,"Chisimu Uwwe ni Ŵatukupelekaga umi ni chiwa, soni Kukwetu ni kwakuwujila."
  50,44,"Lisiku lyaliichaaganjichila litaka (kuti akopochemo) mwachitema-chitema, wele ni nsonganganyo wakwepepala nnope Kukwetu."
  50,45,"Uwwe tukumanyilila chenene yaakuŵecheta. Soni mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nganim’ba ŵakwakanganichisya ŵanganyao (ku chikulupi). Basi munkumbusyani ni Qur’an jwaakogopa chitetelo Changu."
  51,37,"Ni twalesile mwalakwemo chilosyo (cha ipotesi jajili mbwani jajiwe) kwa ŵandu ŵaakuijogopa ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  51,38,"Nombe mu (abali ja) Musa (muŵele mwana chilosyo cha ipotesi), pandema jatwantumisye kwa Firiauna ni umboni wakuonechela."
  51,39,"Basi (Firiauna) jwanyosyisye ligongo lya machili gakwe, ni jwatite: “(Aju ni) nsaŵi kapena jwamasoka.”"
  52,28,"“Chisimu uwwe twaliji kala (ku duniya) tuli nkum’bomba (Jwele Jikape), chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwambone nnope, Jwachanasa channope.”"
  52,29,"Basi kumbusyani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), soni mmwe nganim’ba abimbi kapena ŵamasoka pa chindimba cha Ambuje ŵenu (champele, wauli utume)."
  52,30,"Kapena ŵanganyao akutiji: “(Jwalakweju ni) nkwiimba ilaanga, tugamba kun’jembechela kuti chimpate chiwa (yachatite pakwapata akwiimba ŵane ŵaakala)?”"
  53,22,"Kwele ni gaŵanya kwalupuso (kwakuntenda lupuso Allah)."
  53,23,"Nganigaŵatu galakwego ikaŵeje menape (ga isanamu) gan’gakolasile jenumanja ni achatati ŵenu, Allah nganatulusya pa yalakweyo umboni uliose (wakundisya kuigalagatila), ngakukuya ŵanganyao ikaŵeje liganichisya, ni yayikusaka mitima, kutendaga pamasile pachaichilile kuumila kwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah) chongoko."
  53,24,"Kapena mundu mpaka akombole kupata chilichose chaakuchiluumba? (Ngwamba!)"
  54,13,"Ni twan’jigele (Nuhujo) pa chombo chamatabwa chachakomedwe ni misomali (jaitela)."
  54,14,"Chaliji nkwenda (mwakuloleledwa) ni meso Getu, kuŵa malipilo kwa ajula juŵaliji ali akaniliidwe (Nuhu)."
  54,15,"Soni chisimu twachilesile (chombocho) kuŵa chilosyo, ana pana ŵaachikumbuchila (ni kuliwunda nacho)?"
  55,7,"Soni liwunde ŵalinyakwile, ni ŵaŵisile chilungamiko."
  55,8,"Kuti mkapungusyaga pa kupima."
  55,9,"Ni n’jimicheje chipiimo mwachilungamiko, soni nkapungusyaga yakupimidwa."